purpose:
(Clinical Focus: This value set identifies antipsychotic medications.),(Data Element Scope: This value set was intended to map to the QDM data type of medication.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes codes that identify antipsychotic medications.),(Exclusion Criteria: Does not include prochlorperazine, for its use in treating nausea. Does not include medications that are not available in the US.
Does not include antipsychotic combinations with antidepressant medications.)
